<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
		<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no,address=no">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Style-Type" content="text/css">
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Script-Type" content="text/javascript">
		<title>葬儀一覧｜コスモスターズ</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/bulma.min.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style.css">
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery.slim.min.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<header class="header">
				<a href="http://www.cosmostars.co.jp/index.html" class="header-link"></a>
			</header>
			<section class="main">
				<div class="main-title">
					<h1 class="main-title-main-font">田中太郎様のお葬儀</h1>
					<p>
						<span class="main-title-sub-text">葬儀時間:<span>17:00</span>開始　</span>
						<span class="main-title-sub-text">ホール名:<span>ハクゼンホール安茂里会館</span></span>
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="">
					<h2 class="sub-title">商品一覧</h2>
					<div class="columns">
						<div class="column is-full-mobile is-4-desktop">
							<div class="card">
								<div class="card-image">
									<figure class="image">
										<img alt="" src="img/tomurai_main.jpg">
									</figure>
								</div>
								<div class="card-content">
									<div class="content">
										<table class="table">
											<tbody>
												<tr>
													<th>商品名</th>
													<th>価格(税込み)</th>
												</tr>
												<tr>
													<td>遥</td>
													<td>2200円</td>
												</tr>
											</tbody>
										</table>
										<p class="card-footer-item"><a class="button">詳細を見る</a></p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="card-footer">
									<form action="index.html">
										<div class="field">
											<div class="control">
												<button class="button">送る</button>
											</div>
										</div>
									</form>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<footer class="footer">
				<div class="has-text-centered">
					<p class="footer-company">株式会社 コスモスターズ</p>
					<p class="footer-address">〒170-0013  東京都豊島区東池袋2-39-2</p>
					<p class="footer-tel">TEL03-3982-6226</p>
				</div>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>